Package com.rvandoosselaer.blocks

Interface ShapeIds

  • public interface ShapeIds
    Contains all the keys of the shapes that are registered in the ShapeRegistry. Use these keys to retrieve the shapes from the ShapeRegistry.get(String).

      • SQUARE_CUBOID_NINE_TENTHS

        static final java.lang.String SQUARE_CUBOID_NINE_TENTHS
        This is a special shape. Although it is not a cube, it is considered as a cube in the visible face check algorithm of a chunk. Blocks with this shape that are next to each other will not render the shared face between them, even if the 'shared' faces are not connected.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
